QuestData.Title: Salvage the Supplies
QuestData.Description: Listen, $n. We can't let our supplies get destroyed.$B$BWith Gilneas walled off from the outside world, we won't last through winter if we lose much more of our stock.$B$BPlease help me salvage what you can.
QuestData.RewardText: Excellent! I'll make sure these get taken to a safe place.
